llx-external-routing (0.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * NetworkManager dispatcher for automatic routing setup.
  * Configurable domains and interfaces via config file.
  * Systemd timer for periodic IP refresh.
  * Support for tailscale, anydesk, facebook domains.

